name: Ruby
about: Ruby is a general programming language used primarily for web applications, and other secondary tasks like data analysis and prototyping. Ruby on Rails is a popular software that is used for web applications. Students aspiring to become web developers, or data scientists can pursue Ruby Courses.

name: SQL
about: SQLCourse is a unique SQL tutorial website that not only provides easy-to-understand SQL instructions at your correct level, but it allows you to practice what you learn using the online SQL interpreter.

name: SEO
about: This course covers the basics of how a website is structured, how search engines work, what they are looking for, choosing competitive keywords, writing content for your website, code optimization, link building, social media and some advanced optimization techniques.
